		<main id="main" class="site-main" role="main"><article id="post-107" class="post-107 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-educational-technology category-technologies-for-classroom-education tag-technology"><header class="entry-header"><h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://paveacademy.org/how-technology-can-be-used-in-learning-and-teaching/" rel="bookmark">How technology can be used in learning and teaching?</a></h2>				<div class="entry-meta">
			<span class="posted-on"><a href="http://paveacademy.org/how-technology-can-be-used-in-learning-and-teaching/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published" datetime="2018-11-21T06:29:43+00:00">November 21, 2018</time><time class="updated" datetime="2019-01-05T15:57:04+00:00">January 5, 2019</time></a></span><span class="byline"> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://paveacademy.org/author/rick-gerson/">Rick Gerson</a></span></span>		</div>
			</header><!-- .entry-header --><div class="entry-content">
		
					<p style="text-align: justify;"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-134" src="http://paveacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Learning-technology.jpg" alt="" width="800" height="400" srcset="http://paveacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Learning-technology.jpg 800w, http://paveacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Learning-technology-300x150.jpg 300w, http://paveacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Learning-technology-768x384.jpg 768w, http://paveacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Learning-technology-360x180.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px">Technology has been used in various changes and development and helps to accomplish vast improvements in productivity. It is utilized to support learning and teaching. Technology has changed classrooms with modern learning tools like handheld devices and computers. It has expanded course offerings, learning materials,and experiences. It has paved the way to offer classes on all days of the week and round the clock. It has helped in building 21st-century talents and skills. It increases motivation and student engagement and speeds up learning.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Technology has the capacity to change teaching by bringing a new model of associated teaching. The new model connects teachers to students and also to specialized content, systems,and resources to assist them in improving instruction and distinguish learning.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Utilizing open <a href="https://scholarship-positions.com/category/masters-scholarships/">educational resources</a> and online learning opportunities and other associated technologies can enhance educational productivity. It accelerates the learning rate, reduce expenses connected with program delivery or instructional materials and utilize teacher time in a better way.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">The virtual or online schools functions for full time and students can enroll and study full time. The students attending online schools obtain all the instructions and earn credits via online. It is completely different from a regular school. It offers blended learning opportunities that provide both online learning and face to face learning opportunities.</p>
