			<span class="posted-on"><a href="http://paveacademy.org/know-the-value-of-education/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published" datetime="2018-08-29T06:00:06+00:00">August 29, 2018</time><time class="updated" datetime="2018-11-22T06:54:00+00:00">November 22, 2018</time></a></span><span class="byline"> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://paveacademy.org/author/rick-gerson/">Rick Gerson</a></span></span>		</div>
			</header><!-- .entry-header --><div class="entry-content">
		
					<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-121" src="http://paveacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Know-the-Value-of-Education.jpg" alt="Know the Value of Education" width="800" height="400" srcset="http://paveacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Know-the-Value-of-Education.jpg 800w, http://paveacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Know-the-Value-of-Education-300x150.jpg 300w, http://paveacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Know-the-Value-of-Education-768x384.jpg 768w, http://paveacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Know-the-Value-of-Education-360x180.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px"></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Education is a powerful weapon which every person should poses. Education offers knowledge and experience to the learner. It makes you a complete person. If a person spends the majority of time in learning and gaining knowledge, the society would definitely look the person in a different way. The person will get additional respect and honour due to the education. Happiness, welfare, sincerity and prosperity hide beneath the shadow of education.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">People dress up well and behave so matured. It is hard to know what is blending inside their brains. Words do not create people’s appearances but it creates good looks, touches, smells,and feelings. Words are powerful and it has the ability to create satisfaction, respect and love.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">It has the power to create anything or change the situation. Words are direct replication of opinions and thoughts. It shows how a person thinks. Whatever a person thinks in his/her mind, it is known by their words.<br>
In the present scenario, people are using words without any concern. If they are cautious that words can break as well as unite several things, they would learn to use wisely. Education offers a clear hope on life. It provides progress, opportunity and clear perspective about life.</p>
